{
  "texts": [
    "4.1: System PromptsThe first prompt that we used was extremely restrictive.",
    "It forced the chatbot to simply not answer if the background information did not contain relevant information:You are helping to answer questions about a lab.",
    "The following background may be useful to you, but it may not be.",
    "Try to base your response in the background information as much as you can.",
    "If the background information does not contain any relevant information to the query, simply say so."
  ]
}